[/quote]
This is usually caused because you forgot to end a line somewhere with a semicolon, or you forgot to close off a bracket or something a long that line. Also, the .length() method is usually used on an array or a string. If this .length isn’t applyed to something like that then it simply won’t do anything. Fix it…[/quote]
